      "Name": "BLA",
      "CategoryID": "@lookup:MJ: AI Agent Categories.Name=Assistant",
      "Description": "BLA (Betty Layered Assembler). Flow Agent that assembles a multi-block, multi-role chat-style prompt by selecting the most specific betty.PromptComponent rows for a given AIPrompt + Organization + Instance, then hands the assembled ChatMessage[] to AIPromptRunner.ExecutePrompt and returns the response. Inputs (via initial agent payload): PromptName (string), OrganizationID (UUID, optional), InstanceID (UUID, optional), ConversationHistory (JSON ChatMessage[], optional). Outputs (on payload): ResponseText, PromptRunID, TokensUsed, Cost.",
